(a) Ms Britt LUNDBERG, member of the Åland Legislative Assembly, is hereby appointed a member in place of Mr Hasse SVENSSON;
(b) Ms Carina AALTONEN, member of the Åland Legislative Assembly, is hereby appointed an alternate member in place of Ms Britt LUNDBERG,
for the remainder of their term of office, which runs until 25 January 2006.
